com.tailf.ned

Class NedCapability

  • Object
    • com.tailf.ned.NedCapability

  • public class NedCapability
extends Object
    NedCapability is used to communicate the capabilities (supported namespace, revision, features and deviations) of a NedConnection (NedGeneric or NedCli).
